summary: The module defines a benchmark that trains a GraphSAGE model in an unsupervised manner using negative sampling, measuring execution time and throughput. It includes a custom loss, a negative sample generator, the model architecture, and utilities for ...
business_intent: The benchmark aims to evaluate the performance and scalability of the GraphSAGE model in an unsupervised setting, providing insights into its computational efficiency and suitability for large-scale graph data processing.
